front.title: •I Will Not Defer
front.gametext: Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to add 2 to your next Force drain at a battleground this turn. If a peace agenda here, once per turn you may activate up to 2 Force when opponent initiates battle.
front.lore: 'I've come before you to resolve this attack on our sovereignty now.'

pulledBy: We Wish To Board At Once
